==================
Basic Commands
==================
** Navigation **
Go <Direction> - Go Living Room

** ITEMS, WEAPONS **
Get <Item>  - Get Hammer
Drop <Item> - Drop Hammer
Look <Item> - Look Hammer
Open<Furniture> - Open Refrigerator

** TALK **
Talk <Character> - Talk Chris

** OTHER **
ATTACK Skombie - attack skombie with current weapon
SECURE ROOM - In order to secure the room you are in
Inventory - returns your inventory details
Help - returns this page if you get stuck
Quit - quit the current game
